## Directory layout

* `/apps/extension` – Chrome MV3 code
* `/apps/dashboard` – Next.js dashboard (voice-ui-kit + flows)
* `/apps/agent`     – Python Pipecat agent
* `/infra/`         – Terraform & Kubernetes manifests
* `/scripts/`       – Dev helpers
* `/docs/`          – ADRs & diagrams

## Branch naming

```
feat/<ticket>-<slug>   fix/<ticket>-<slug>  
chore/<ticket>-<slug>  hotfix/<slug>
```

## Commit messages (Conventional Commits)

```
type(scope)!: short description
```

Examples:
`feat(agent): add pointer overlay processor`
`fix(extension): correct pointer jitter on 4K screens`
